  <official_title>Immunogenicity of the DTaP-IPV-HBV/Hib Combination Vaccine Infanrix Hexa and the Heptavalent Pneumococcal Conjugate Vaccine Prevenar in Pediatric Recipients of Allogeneic Haematopoietic Stem Cell Transplantation</official_title>
