  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the immunogenicity and tolerability of the
      DTaP-IPV-HBV/Hib combination vaccine Infanrix hexa and the heptavalent pneumococcal conjugate
      vaccine Prevenar in pediatric recipients of allogeneic haematopoietic stem cell
      transplantation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
